{"tid":2385236,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（安心出行）約翰遜：向持BNO港人提供在英生活、工作和安居的新途徑感到自豪","createTime":"2021-01-29T02:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T09:01:24.000Z","uid":184679,"like":54,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"faddde1623faddce4507085447de4e46ceedc912","tid":2385236,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T02:35:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/intnews/20210129/photo/bkn-20210129083359986-0129_00992_001_01p.jpg?20210129101550\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fintnews%2F20210129%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210129083359986-0129_00992_001_01p.jpg%3F20210129101550&h=d509dae2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國政府將於當地下周日（31日）開放讓持英國國民（海外）護照（BNO）的香港人申請BNO居留簽證，該國外交部周四（28日）公布詳情，相關持有人可於2月23日起使用手機應用程式申請，並延長「特許入境許可（LOTR）」至3月底。<br />\n<br />\n因應香港去年實施《港區國安法》，英國政府宣布向持BNO港人及其受養人提供入籍途徑，可透過LOTR提前抵英，為期6個月，下周日起可與家人申請特別簽證在英國居留。外交部公布的方案指，下月23日起持BNO港人，以及其持BNO、香港特區護照或歐洲經濟區（EEA）附生物特徵護照的合資格家屬，可利用手機應用程式掃瞄其護照及完成申請，整個過程可在家完成。今次是英國政府首次容許非EEA公民透過手機應用程式申請。<br />\n<br />\n英方又指，去年7月15日至今年1月13日期間，約7,000名持BNO港人及其受養人透過LOTR抵英，政府決定延長有關許可以配合新簽證計劃完全數碼化，特許入境者毋須立即申請新簽證。另外，申請5年期BNO居留簽證的費用為每人250英鎊（約2,658港元），申請人亦可申請逗留30個月，費用為每人180英鎊（約1,913港元）。<br />\n<br />\n英國首相約翰遜發聲明指，英方向持BNO港人提供在英生活、工作和安居的新途徑，對此感自豪。英方重視與港人之間的深厚歷史聯繫和友誼，捍衞自由和自治，這是英國和香港都重視的價值。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on. cc/hk/bkn/cnt/intnews/20210129/bkn-20210129083359986-0129_00992_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"edcc16d8a1d023b02b5c8d1cc1cce6213abf2be0","tid":2385236,"uid":92448,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T02:41:16.000Z","msg":"呢啲感到自豪同班支那曱甴官畀人制裁感到光榮真係冇得比"},{"pid":"cd94460ef22eca708ebfe2ecc3a5a29cfd0b0115","tid":2385236,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T02:46:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8129c4b9a6465134573a37d04cb19eacda489890","tid":2385236,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e080a9999512e505a60b6742845510bd3abcd3e8","tid":2385236,"uid":179775,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:05:36.000Z","msg":"約7,000名持BNO港人及其受養人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"906a75903a12d9356c6a8438790bc07feb235997","tid":2385236,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:20:14.000Z","msg":"無BNO人士都想多謝佢"},{"pid":"7718263e856e02e612fd0cc0e8c0b3f1afe6d362","tid":2385236,"uid":48088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:21:25.000Z","msg":"歷史會記住係邊一個首相俾留居海外的英國人回家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca223bbe28344f40c9964b333d10a56acc909e8","tid":2385236,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e080a9999512e505a60b6742845510bd3abcd3e8","tid":2385236,"uid":179775,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:05:36.000Z","msg":"約7,000名持BNO港人及其受養人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:22: